# ChartStreamAnimator - Live Data Visualizer

ChartStreamAnimator is perfect for quickly visualizing trends in data received from APIs, sensors, or simulations.

## Features
- Matplotlib-powered  
- Live chart updates  
- Simple and clean interface  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/22_ChartStreamAnimator.git
cd 22_ChartStreamAnimator
python visualize.py
